msgstr ""

#: ../restored/firestormwall.rst:92
msgid ""
":game:`Ares` restores the two map actions related to the Firestorm "
"Defense from :game:`Tiberian Sun`. Map actions 92 and 93 activate and "
"deactivate the Firestorm Walls unconditionally, and while it is active "
"from these map actions, it will not drain the charge and thus stay active"
" indefinitely."
